## Summary
- SimpleCreep wrapper exposes harvesting, movement, combat, logistics, and utility helpers for single-room Screeps bases.
- Resource helpers cover finding/picking up energy, filling spawn/extensions, and storing overflow.
- Utility helpers include memory accessors, status logging, tick callbacks, and role-based dispatch/iteration utilities.
- PopulationManager handles deterministic body selection, spawn requests, and per-role population maintenance helpers.
